Darkfate/Aelo/Celeno/ocipite::

Circuits installed inside Darkfate's shuttles allowed Darkfate knows 
what was goin on in battle. When he knew that some of Killfest's team 
were in danger he send a special shuttle with a pilot: Aelo.

She was the best pilot in BlackFortress and she controled now the 
best shuttle in that Base. Soon Aelo left the base.
